All matches of qualification stage were played in Belo Horizonte at neutral venues:
- America never played at Alameda stadium;
- Atletico never played at Antenio Carlos stadium;
- Cruzeiro never played at JK stadium;
- Sete de Setembro never played at Independencia stadium.


