[Mar 13]
Bela Vista       1-3  Siderergica

[Mar 29]
Uberaba          1-2  America
[match played originally in March 1st, a 2-2 tie. However, as both teams pursued a victory in order
to play a tiebreak with Cruzeiro for the second stage title, they used the referee's match report,
that stated that the goal bars were not within legal measures, to annull the match and reschedule
it. After weeks of discussion with FMF, Cruzeiro and Atletico, the other interested parties, the
match was rescheduled, America won it and qualified to the tiebreak.]

